e\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SOI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silicon_on_insulator\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silicon_on_insulator\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.17092765489809e-21, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\", \"score\": 0.9999999986730472, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caribbean Initiative\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6152453109439623e-22, \"text\": \"Diplomacy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomacy\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993331373360432, \"rank\": 0.0006176276451484282, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The programme\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"the US Department\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"State\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US-based Coulston noted that the trip to Jamaica, which is scheduled to end this weekend, is a priceless engagement for Special Olympics athletes and volunteers.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\", \"score\": 0.9999999966084943, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coulston\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\"}, {\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999848892073536, \"rank\": 7.664041809171183e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.17092765489809e-21, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trip\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"a priceless engagement\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While on the island, the delegation will visit schools and cultural sites and engage in leadership and unified sports activities.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the island\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the delegation\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural sites\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"leadership\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"unified sports activities\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so excited for this week-long immersive experience for us to engage in leadership development opportunities, participate in unified sports - in which youth with and without disabilities are playing together - as well as being able to form lifelong friendships,\\\" he told theJamaica Observer.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this week-long immersive experience\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"leadership development opportunities\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"unified sports\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"youth\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"disabilities\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"lifelong friendships\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"theJamaica Observer\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said staging unified sports in schools is central to bringing about global inclusion.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unified sports\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"global inclusion\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We see unified sports as people with and without intellectual disabilities playing together and we know that it helps them to experience joy, demonstrate courage, and it helps to form friendships on and off the field,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unified sports\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"intellectual disabilities\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"demonstrate courage\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"friendships\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are able to exemplify that strength and growth, then back in the community it will be the norm\\u2026 that's unified living, doing everything together regardless of challenges or even your abilities.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that strength\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"growth\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"unified living\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"even your abilities\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's really important to help foster those inclusive environments that can really begin at the school level to grow those positive mindsets and behaviours where inclusion is the norm,\\\" Coulston added.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\", \"score\": 0.9999999966084943, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coulston\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coulston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those inclusive environments\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the school level\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"those positive mindsets\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"behaviours\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said there were positives from the visit to Washington, DC where the SOJ delegation was exposed to local culture and food and given a broader insight into inclusion initiatives.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"positives\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"the visit\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"Washington\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"DC\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"the SOJ delegation\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"local culture\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"a broader insight\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion initiatives\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a really great experience for everyone involved because we were at one together, sharing everything together and growing together.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really great experience\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some [young athletes] can be shy and timid but the exchange programme helps to grow their confidence and grow their belief in themselves as leaders.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some [young athletes\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the exchange programme\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"their confidence\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"their belief\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is very important because typically in society we tend to think of leaders as the most outspoken\\u2026 but in reality all of us can be and are leaders,\\\" he reasoned.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2544}]}]}"